In the Baseline, carbon emissions grow from 478 MtC in 1997 to 700 MtC in 2020, a growth of 46.5 percent over the period.
Similarly, energy use rises from 25.0 Quads in 1997 to 36.8 Quads in 2020, a 47.2 percent growth (Fig. 6.3).
